{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"e0904ed439","title":"给毛岸英、毛岸青的信","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"e5ff37f87c","index":0,"year":1938,"month":3,"day":4,"articleId":"e0904ed439"}],"tags":[{"id":"2a70b5d939","name":"书信","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji12","name":"毛泽东全集第12卷","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives8/main/mao-quanji/maoquanji12.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji12":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"106786a5ea","type":"paragraph","text":"给毛岸英、毛岸青的信”","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji12","articleId":"e0904ed439"},{"id":"75a7bc791a","type":"paragraph","text":"（1938年3月4日）亲爱的岸英、岸青时常想念你们，知道你们情形尚好，有进步，并接到了你们的照片，十分欢喜。现因有便，托致此信，也希望你们写信给我，我是盼望你们来信啊！我的情形还好。以后有机会再写信给你们。祝你们健康，愉快，与进步！","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji12","articleId":"e0904ed439"},{"id":"18cf17ba05","type":"paragraph","text":"毛泽东","index":2,"publicationId":"maoquanji12","articleId":"e0904ed439"},{"id":"5e1a77d3e6","type":"paragraph","text":"三月四日[1]1937年年初，岸英、岸青到莫斯科学习。1938年年初，有人从莫便写了这封能，托人带到莫斯科。","index":3,"publicationId":"maoquanji12","articleId":"e0904ed439"}],"page":{"id":"1ca7c5ffc8","publicationId":"maoquanji12","articleId":"e0904ed439","start":69,"end":69}}}},"__N_SSG":true}